| colspan="5" align=left | This is the first ever series of collectors' coins issued by Slovenia, specially for this occasion honouring the presidency of the European Union. 

In the [[Obverse and reverse|obverse]] the coin shows a "dynamic" EU star in the form of a windmill. This star represents Slovenia's initiative, movement, energy, volition, strength and active role during the EU presidency. There is an inscription on the coin, ''Facta loquuntur'' ("works speak"), indicating results and success. 

On the [[Obverse and reverse|reverse]], 27 dynamic stars, one for each of the 27 EU Member States, can be observed.
